Maintainer: Yunpeng Zhou <u3514104@connect.hku.hk>
Description: Penalized and non-penalized frailty model fitting with Clustered data, multi-event data and recurrent data. 'LASSO', 'MCP' and 'SCAD' penalized regression can be fitted, the model is efficiently fitted using 'MM' algorithm. The technique is based on the paper,
    Huang et al. (2022) <doi:10.3390/math10040538>,
    Huang et al. (2023) <doi:10.1177/09622802221133554>.
